<section class="section reveal" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="sl">How It Works</div>
      <h2>Install. Enable. Go.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">01</div><div><h3>Install from Google Play</h3><p>Download BotPilot and open it. No account creation, no sign-up, no API keys needed.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">02</div><div><h3>Enable the Accessibility Service</h3><p>Grant BotPilot the Accessibility Service permission, same as screen readers use. This lets it see and tap Instagram's UI.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">03</div><div><h3>Pick a mode and set your rates</h3><p>Choose Stories, Feed, Location, or Hashtag. Adjust the rate sliders for likes, GIF reacts, emoji reactions, and comment likes.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-num">04</div><div><h3>Hit start and put it down</h3><p>BotPilot opens Instagram and works through your session automatically. Watch the live log or just let it run in your pocket.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

